<![CDATA[<div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please do not respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your local staffing team.&nbsp;</span></font></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b><br></b></span></font></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</span></font></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b><br></b></span></font></div><div><font size="2"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">I am writing to inform you that you have been entered into the workplace pension scheme. This is new legislation which the government has introduced this year - it is a way of saving for your retirement that's arranged by your employer. For further information about the scheme, please go to&nbsp;</span></font><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a href="www.gov.uk/workplace-pensions">www.gov.uk/workplace-pensions</a></span></font></div><div><font size="2"><br></font></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">All staff are entered into the pension scheme if they fulfill the criteria for auto-enrollment. For a full list of criteria please refer to the <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/frequently-asked-questions/">Staffing Website FAQ 7.3.</a></span></font></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></div><div><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="